title: Command And Conquer Red Alert II - Ultimate Collection
description:
Red alert 2 - The ultimate collection version

It comes with yuri's revenge but good luck getting it to run on x64




You just run the RA2 file or set it as the directory for gameranger to play 

multiplayer.

It comes with the wsock64.dll hack to play through networking on windows vista+.

There are multiple threads you can google if you have issues starting the game.

But most of you shouldn't have a problem.
